
Make sure the following conditions are met before using this module:
1. Install antiword
2. Make sure you symlink from /usr/bin/antiword to the actual executable
3. Make a directory /usr/share/antiword and put the text mapping files there which came
   with the distribution of antiword.

In the rulelist of the router you can append the following line:

default;DNTCR;mimetype;application/msword;DNTCR;ACT_FORWARD;antiword;

